A Fleek account (sign up at https://fleek.co)
Basic knowledge of Git and hosting
Log in to Fleek Dashboard: https://app.fleek.co.
Click on "New Site".
Choose "GitHub" and authenticate Fleek with your GitHub account.
Select your website repository and branch to deploy.
Set the build command (e.g., npm run build, gatsby build, etc.).
Specify the output directory (e.g., build/, dist/, etc.).
Click Deploy Site.
